A simple Ram backed block device driver for having fun
   
After installation of the module, a device called 'rbd0' will show up at 
/dev/ dir and can be used as other block devices(e.g: use fdisk and mkfs,
you can create partitions and file systems on this device.). 
 
=====
Compile:
	$ make
Install:
	$ sudo make install
destall:
	$ sudo make destall
reinstall:
	$ sudo reinstall

====
